s, s, open sack, put pack and matches and axe in sack, get canteen, get sack,
n, n, n, n, break lock with rock, get lock, drop lock and rock, open trunk, 
get beef and map, s, w, w, drink, open canteen,fill canteen, close canteen, e
, e, e, s, s, e, e, dig in sand, again, again, again,again, unfold map, put 
