to SEVERED ARMS, TALK TO EILEAIN, leave and talk to MALLIN <the guy in green 
clothes>, he'll give you METAL BAR, go with it to VILLAGE SHOP, and GIVE IT 
TO EWAN, he'll give you some money and GEM.  Go to MAGPIE TAVERN, TALK TO 
