wine...  Now go left to THE GATE ROOM and USE FAT ON LEVER, TELL MINNOW TO 
OPERATE LEVER, while he does it, PULL WINCH. The gate will open..  Now go 
back, and make sure to save the game <AGAIN>, because you may have some pro-
blems on the bridge..  After you pass him, head to the left so you'll see Se-
lena..

